title: Spyforce - 16 - The Saviour (1)(1972).avi
description:
Erskine and Adolf are sent to a remote hospital in Papua New Guinea to retrieve Dr Wayne Brookman, a pacifist who believes he is safe from the Japanese and the local people as he treats both military and civilian personnel alike.

Brookman was involved in the production of 'heavy water' prior to the war, so it is essential they get him out - preferably alive.

NOTE: This is part one of a two part episode.

(Part two airs here in Australia on Tuesday July 14, 2009 at 1am. It will be available shortly after it airs)
